name: Ozsale
overview:
About Ozsale Ozsale is the number 1 members-only online shopping club in Australia and your doorway to affordable designer fashion.

Every day we host sales for the top fashion brands in the world. Ozsale members can access these sales and enjoy savings of up to 80% on ladies, men’s and children’s fashion and accessories as well as beauty and homeware brands.

Membership is free and everyone is welcome to join.

Ozsale is part of the APAC Sale Group.

Ozsale has dedicated buyers in Australia, Europe, Asia and New Zealand who spend their days (and sometimes nights!) searching the world for the best products and negotiating deals direct with suppliers to offer exclusively to our members.

Ozsale provides a convenient way to access sales all year round from the comfort of your own home. With Ozsale, you no longer need to wait for the sales because the best brands are always on sale!

How does it work? It’s simple! Ozsale members receive a sale notification every morning.

New sales are held each day, seven days a week. Sales start each morning and typically run for 2 to 3 days.

60% of stock is usually sold in the first 48 hours so getting in early is key!

Flash sales disappear from the site once they are finished.

How to join? Membership is free and for a limited time only, anyone can join!

Only a limited number of memberships are available. When all the spots are taken, membership will be on an invitation-only basis.

So, if you never want to pay full price again for designer fashion, join Ozsale today and access our exclusive online sales.

Where else can you find us? Ozsale is part of the APAC Sale Group, operating in New Zealand (nzsale.co.nz), Singapore (singsale.com.sg) and Malaysia (mysale.my) where our members are equally enthusiastic about the great brands on sale and jaw dropping savings.

Planning for continued expansion throughout Asia is underway so stay tuned!
